      "page_number": 2,
      "parent_id": "c037eec686638df7612b2b740ad58c5c",
      "filetype": "application/pdf"
    }
  },
  {
    "type": "ListItem",
    "element_id": "3e46c252a69f4b3269df22222fa01636",
    "text": "In this chapter, we show that the modeling techniques of Chapters 2 and 3 can be combined, yielding what are known as hybrid systems.",
