    }
  },
  {
    "type": "ListItem",
    "element_id": "31fdc960479fd528908de75e045ae3ff",
    "text": "A hybrid system associates with each state of an FSM a dynamic behavior, called \u201cstate refinements\u201d that gives the dynamic behavior of the output as a function of the input and (possibly) additional continuous state variables.",
