      "filetype": "application/pdf"
    }
  },
  {
    "type": "ListItem",
    "element_id": "99237f1da42819c21c66a2113a48d463",
    "text": "Such a control signal could directly drive a heater. \u2022 Each state has a refinement that gives the value of the output h while the state machine is in that state.",
