    }
  },
  {
    "type": "NarrativeText",
    "element_id": "dc026a1d1503fa148da79c9ad8db7809",
    "text": "Classes of Hybrid Systems: 1- Timed Automata \u2022 Most cyber-physical systems require measuring the passage of time and performing actions at specific times.",
